<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Invoice Customer Email</title>

</head>
<body style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative; font-family: Tahoma; direction: rtl; background-color: #eeeeee; margin: 0; padding: 0;" bgcolor="#eeeeee">
<style type="text/css">
    *::before { -webkit-box-sizing: border-box !important; -moz-box-sizing: border-box !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; }
    *::after { -webkit-box-sizing: border-box !important; -moz-box-sizing: border-box !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline !important; }
    </style>

<div style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative; width: 600px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100px; border-bottom-width: 2px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #16a085; -webkit-border-radius: 0 0 0.3rem 0.3rem; -moz-border-radius: 0 0 0.3rem 0.3rem; border-radius: 0 0 0.3rem 0.3rem; background-color: white; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0;">
    <div style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative; width: 600px; max-width: 100%; height: 50px; line-height: 40px; background-color: white; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5px 10px;">
        <img src="<%- config.url.origin %>/public/images/logo-black.png" alt="storm-logo" style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; float: right; height: 40px; width: auto;" align="right">
        <a style="float: left; font-size: 14px; color: blue; -webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none;" href="<%- config.url.origin %>"><%- config.url.origin %></a>
    </div>
    <div style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative; width: 100%; height: 110px; line-height: 50px; color: white; text-align: center; background-color: #2ecc71;" align="center">
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; max-height: 50px; font-size: 30px; overflow: hidden; color: #303030; margin: 0 auto;"><%-  %></span>
        <img src="<%- config.url.origin + branchLogo %>" alt="branch-logo" style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative; width: 200px; height: auto; text-align: center; margin: 0 auto;">
    </div>
    <div style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; display: block; width: 100%; min-height: 50px; line-height: 32px; margin: 0; padding: 30px 10px 25px;">
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">سلام <%- detailAccountDisplay %></span><br style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">فاکتور صادر شده برای شما از طریق لینک زیر قابل دسترسی می باشد.</span><br style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">باتشکر</span><br style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <a href="<%- invoiceUrl %>" target="_blank" style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box; color: white; text-decoration: none !important; display: block; position: relative !important; -webkit-border-radius: 0.3rem; -moz-border-radius: 0.3rem; border-radius: 0.3rem; line-height: 40px; max-width: 250px; height: 50px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; vertical-align: middle; border-bottom-width: 3px; background-color: #1abc9c; margin: 10px auto; padding: 5px 10px; border-color: #16a085; border-style: none none solid;">نمایش فاکتور</a>
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">شماره ی فاکتور: <%- number %></span><br style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <span style="-webkit-box-sizing: border-box; -moz-box-sizing: border-box; box-sizing: border-box;">تاریخ: <%- date %></span>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
